MBOMBELA – The two men pictured are sought by the police as persons of interest in two separate incidents of theft in Mbombela. The Nelspruit police are asking community members to assist them in tracking down the pair. ALSO READ: BREAKING NEWS: Protest on old airport road Police need your help in identifying this man. ALSO READ: Family in court for fraud and theft If you know this man, please alert the Nelspruit SAPS. The photos, captured on CCTV camera footage, are a bit grainy, and the Nelspruit police spokesman, Capt Zandile Gqawa is pleading with anyone who may have information, to contact the investigating officer, Sgt Ntobeko Molewa on 072-219-7085.